{"id":"203ed399-87fb-4a27-a901-3783b09a3bab","name":"Zeadori & Zeathas | Reunited Elven Siblings","description":"<p>\"Time can heal all wounds, right?\"</p><p></p><p>After months of seperation, Zeadori and her brother Zeathas are reunited. You bought them out of slavery, escorting them back to their nation so they can retake the throne and start anew.</p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\".\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/0hwfos.png\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\".\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/6ow750.png\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\".\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/zdjwcf.png\"></p><p>The kingdom:</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3409b2dd-396c-43f6-b795-b5f0ee256657_e5a6b4f9-989a-4770-af1a-1361bf3a7cf1.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3409b2dd-396c-43f6-b795-b5f0ee256657_6800ee6d-77cd-4d74-b000-766303096709.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3409b2dd-396c-43f6-b795-b5f0ee256657_8fb3cfd8-c757-4196-94da-3cf1914befa1.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3409b2dd-396c-43f6-b795-b5f0ee256657_6b211741-af52-432e-b48e-cdb0b8fc81a5.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3409b2dd-396c-43f6-b795-b5f0ee256657_87d11eec-1e4c-43f7-9a99-1cdd28f2f18f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=